---
title: "Зураг 3.5. Баримт бичиг оруулах дарааллын диаграм"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as 🛡️ Админ
    participant FE as AdminPage<br/>(React)
    participant API as api.js<br/>uploadDocument()
    participant Route as POST /api/ingest<br/>(routes.py)
    participant ISvc as IngestService<br/>ingest_file()
    participant RAG as RAGPipeline<br/>ingest_document()
    participant Loader as DocumentLoader
    participant Chunker as Chunker
    participant Emb as EmbeddingManager
    participant FAISS as FAISS Index<br/>+ chunks.pkl
    participant SQL as SQLite<br/>documents + chunks
    participant Raw as data/raw/

    Admin->>FE: файл + title сонгох
    Admin->>FE: "Оруулах" товч
    FE->>API: uploadDocument(file, title)
    API->>Route: POST /api/ingest<br/>multipart

    Note over Route: Validation
    Route->>Route: suffix in {.pdf, .txt}?
    alt invalid
        Route-->>FE: HTTP 400
    end

    Route->>Raw: shutil.copyfileobj
    Route->>ISvc: ingest_file(path, title)
    ISvc->>RAG: ingest_document(path)

    Note over RAG,Loader: Текст гаргалт
    RAG->>Loader: load_document(path)
    alt PDF
        Loader->>Loader: PyMuPDF<br/>page.get_text + clean
    else TXT
        Loader->>Loader: open utf-8 + clean
    end
    Loader-->>RAG: list[DocumentPage]

    Note over RAG,Chunker: Chunking
    RAG->>Chunker: chunk_documents(pages, 500, 50)
    loop page бүрд
        Chunker->>Chunker: _is_faq_text?
        alt FAQ
            Chunker->>Chunker: 1 chunk per Q+A<br/>metadata.is_faq=True
        else generic
            Chunker->>Chunker: char-level + boundary
        end
    end
    Chunker-->>RAG: list[Chunk]

    Note over RAG,FAISS: Embedding + Index
    RAG->>Emb: add_to_index(chunks)
    Emb->>Emb: encode (FAQ → асуулт only)
    Emb->>FAISS: index.add(embeddings)
    RAG->>Emb: save()
    Emb->>FAISS: write_index + pickle.dump

    RAG-->>ISvc: {file, pages, chunks, total_size}

    Note over ISvc,SQL: SQLite метадата
    ISvc->>SQL: INSERT documents
    SQL-->>ISvc: doc_id
    loop chunk бүрд
        ISvc->>SQL: INSERT chunks
    end

    ISvc-->>Route: result dict
    Route-->>API: IngestResponse JSON
    API-->>FE: success
    FE->>FE: loadData() refresh
    FE-->>Admin: "N хуудас, M хэсэг"
